Tony Seruga
@TonySeruga
President Trump reshared a viral clip of Tulsi Gabbard dropping a bombshell: accusing Obama’s top national security team (Brennan, Clapper, Comey, Rice) of orchestrating a “politically manufactured” intel assessment after the 2016 election.

twitter.content:
@spencerpratt Not merely “ok”. 

Anyone who doesn’t love America is a traitor and beneath contempt. 

Those who don’t love America, those who are disloyal should be exiled immediately.

